---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" activePage="about">
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
    <h1>35+ Years of <em>Flavor</em></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">From a family's dream to a University City institution. This is who we are.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"><div class="divider-line"><span>Est. 1987</span></div></div>

  <!-- ABOUT INTRO -->
  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="about-photo">
      <img src="images/front.png" alt="Front photo of International Foods & Spices" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <h2>A Family Store for a Whole Community</h2>
      <p><strong>International Foods & Spices</strong> has been a cornerstone of the University City neighborhood since 1987. Family-owned and operated, we've spent over three decades bringing the flavors of South Asia, the Middle East, and East Africa to Philadelphia.</p>
      <p>What started as a small grocery has grown into a destination — known for our handmade samosas, our fully stocked spice wall, and our selection of halal meats. We serve everyone from the Penn and Drexel students next door to families who've been shopping with us for generations.</p>
      <p>We're not just a store. We're a piece of the neighborhood.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIMELINE -->
  <section class="timeline-section dark">
    <div class="timeline-header">
      <p class="section-label">Our Journey</p>
      <h2>A Brief History</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">1982</div>
        <p>International Foods & Spices opens its first location at 120 S 41st St, bringing South Asian groceries to the University City neighborhood.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">1987</div>
        <p>A new generation comes in. The store moves to its current home at 4203 Walnut Street, a bigger space to better serve the growing community.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">1998</div>
        <p>The store expands at 4203 Walnut Street, adding more square footage and a bigger, greater variety of products — continuing the tradition and expanding the store's offerings to include East African and Middle Eastern products.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">Today</div>
        <p>Still family-owned, still on Walnut Street, still making the best samosas in Philly. Featured in Philadelphia Magazine and loved by a community that spans generations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURED IN -->
<section class="featured-section">
  <p class="section-label">Press</p>
  <h2>As Featured In</h2>
  <p class="featured-subtitle">We're honored to be recognized by Philadelphia's best.</p>
  <div class="featured-badges">
    <a href="https://www.phillymag.com/foobooz/street-food-philly/" target="_blank" class="featured-badge">
      <span class="pub-name">Philadelphia Magazine</span>
      <span class="badge-desc">Philly Street Foods for Eating on the Go</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.phillymag.com/foobooz/best-indian-food-philadelphia/" target="_blank" class="featured-badge">
      <span class="pub-name">Philadelphia Magazine</span>
      <span class="badge-desc">Where to Eat Indian Food in Philadelphia</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>

<style>

  .timeline-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.timeline-header h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--dark);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.timeline {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 3rem;
}

.timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 2px;
  background: var(--border-light);
}

.timeline-item {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
}

.timeline-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

.timeline-item::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: -3rem;
  top: 0.35rem;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--saffron);
  border: 2px solid var(--cream);
  transform: translateX(-4px);
}

.timeline-item .year {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--chili);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.timeline-item p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

  /* ABOUT INTRO */
  .about-intro {
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

.about-photo img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
}

.about-photo {
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  background: var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
}

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--dark);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-text p strong {
    color: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline-section {
  padding: 5rem 3rem;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.timeline-section.dark {
  max-width: 100%;
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--cream);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.timeline-section.dark::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(232, 168, 56, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.timeline-section.dark .timeline-header,
.timeline-section.dark .timeline {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  position: relative;
}

.timeline-section.dark .timeline-header h2 {
  color: var(--cream);
}

.timeline-section.dark .timeline::before {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}

.timeline-section.dark .timeline-item::before {
  border-color: var(--dark);
}

.timeline-section.dark .timeline-item p {
  color: rgba(253, 246, 236, 0.55);
}

  /* FEATURED IN */
  .featured-section {
  padding: 5rem 3rem;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.featured-section h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--dark);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.featured-subtitle {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

.featured-badges {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.featured-badge {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
  background: var(--warm-white);
  border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}

.featured-badge:hover {
  border-color: var(--saffron);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(26, 18, 8, 0.08);
}

.pub-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--dark);
}

.badge-desc {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-weight: 500;
}

  .divider-dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--saffron);
  }

  .pub-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .timeline-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .featured-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>